OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779466274
OL,3,CTraffic light vandalism blamed on
OL,4,C'ridiculous' conspiracy theories
OL,6,FCouncil bosses have condemned damage
OL,7,Fto traffic lights thought to have been
OL,8,Fcarried out by a group of "outlandish"
OL,9,Fconspiracy theorists.
OL,11,FLincolnshire County Council said 10
OL,12,Funits in Sleaford were attacked within
OL,13,Fthe space of a week, costing #8,000 to
OL,14,Frepair.
OL,16,FA group calling themselves "Blade
OL,17,FRunners" have claimed responsibility,
OL,18,Fposting on social media that they were
OL,19,F"fighting off intrusive technology to
OL,20,Fwake up humanity".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779466274
OL,3,CTraffic light vandalism blamed on
OL,4,C'ridiculous' conspiracy theories
OL,6,FThe sensors they removed are mounted
OL,7,Fon lights to help traffic flow.
OL,9,FAnthony Gent, of the council's traffic
OL,10,Fsignal team, said: "The claims made by
OL,11,Fthis group are outlandish at best,
OL,12,Fridiculous at worst."
OL,14,FIn one video showing a traffic light
OL,15,Fbeing tampered with, a man makes the
OL,16,Funverified claim that the group are
OL,17,F"finding phased array weaponry on our
OL,18,Fstreets" adding: "We've decided to
OL,19,Ftake the units down, remove them, make
OL,20,Fit safe for everybody."
OL,26,@rD@TOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779466274
OL,3,CTraffic light vandalism blamed on
OL,4,C'ridiculous' conspiracy theories
OL,6,FIn military terminology, "phased
OL,7,Farrays" are primarily used for
OL,8,Ftracking, targeting, and electronic
OL,9,Fwarfare.
OL,11,FMr Gent said "(The sensors are) here
OL,12,Fto make people's journeys better and
OL,13,Feasier and safer by detecting vehicles
OL,14,Fas they approach junctions and
OL,15,Fcrossings, and also getting people
OL,16,Fsafely across the road.
OL,18,F"By vandalising these sensors,
OL,19,Fbasically you're making this junction
OL,20,Fwork very, very inefficiently."
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@OpmsD@_pnzD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779466274
OL,3,CTraffic light vandalism blamed on
OL,4,C'ridiculous' conspiracy theories
OL,6,FHe said the technology had "been
OL,7,Faround for years" and was "totally
OL,8,Fharmless".
OL,10,F"It's the sort of technology that's
OL,11,Fused in most modern cars, to be
OL,12,Fhonest. If you have adaptive cruise
OL,13,Fcontrol in your car, it uses exactly
OL,14,Fthe same technology," he said.
OL,16,FHe added: "Social media can be a real
OL,17,Fpower for good, but it can also be
OL,18,Fused to misinform and spread
OL,19,Fmisinformation about things.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@KOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779466274
OL,3,CTraffic light vandalism blamed on
OL,4,C'ridiculous' conspiracy theories
OL,6,F"Unfortunately in this case it looks
OL,7,Flike people have picked up on
OL,8,Fsomething which is utterly false and
OL,9,Fthen using that as justification to go
OL,10,Fand vandalise traffic signals and
OL,11,Fcause damage to our assets at great
OL,12,Fcost to us.
OL,14,F"By making the junction less
OL,15,Fefficient, people may be tempted to
OL,16,Frun a red signal, so there's a whole
OL,17,Fhost of issues that can snowball from
OL,18,Fthis. It's important that we get the
OL,19,Fmessage out there that this equipment
OL,20,Fwe're using is totally safe and there
OL,21,Fis no danger to the public whatsoever."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
