PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779466274
OL,3,CTraffic light vandalism blamed on
OL,4,C'ridiculous' conspiracy theories
OL,6,FThe incidents come after about 200
OL,7,Ftraffic light detector units were
OL,8,Fvandalised across Cambridgeshire in
OL,9,Frecent weeks.
OL,11,FIn a statement Lincolnshire Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "These incidents of criminal
OL,13,Fdamage are of real concern and could
OL,14,Fbe dangerous; this is clearly such an
OL,15,Firresponsible thing to do.
OL,17,F"Anyone who has any further video
OL,18,Ffootage or knows anything about this
OL,19,Fshould get in touch with us."
OL,26,@tD@GOUyD@AOU
